211
00:11:14,790 --> 00:11:16,010
which student from our class won the second prize.

212
00:11:16,010 --> 00:11:17,220
she would come after us later.

213
00:11:17,220 --> 00:11:19,570
And which one won the first prize?

214
00:11:21,250 --> 00:11:23,450
Our results were really good this time.

215
00:11:25,480 --> 00:11:27,990
Let's see who won the second prize and who won the first between the two of you.

216
00:11:27,990 --> 00:11:31,170
First, let's congratulate our little English teacher,

217
00:11:31,370 --> 00:11:32,270
Qi Jiahao.

218
00:11:33,790 --> 00:11:35,650
He won the second prize this time.

219
00:11:36,040 --> 00:11:37,660
He performed as expected.

220
00:11:37,990 --> 00:11:40,450
Not bad. Let's give him some encouragement.

221
00:11:43,370 --> 00:11:44,310
What's going on?

222
00:11:44,740 --> 00:11:46,400
One of you didn't win an award?

223
00:11:48,000 --> 00:11:49,320
Next, we have

224
00:11:49,380 --> 00:11:50,460
our class monitor,

225
00:11:50,660 --> 00:11:52,880
Li Yu,

226
00:11:53,200 --> 00:11:55,130
who really surprised me this time.

227
00:11:55,200 --> 00:11:56,260
Congratulations.

228
00:11:58,540 --> 00:11:59,370
It shows that

229
00:11:59,530 --> 00:12:00,490
as long as you performed as expected,

230
00:12:00,490 --> 00:12:03,950
-Neither of you won an award?
-you could achieve good results.

231
00:12:05,370 --> 00:12:09,080
But we had four students participating in the competition.

232
00:12:09,910 --> 00:12:13,990
What about Sheng Wang and Jiang Tian?

233
00:12:15,530 --> 00:12:16,520
I reminded you

234
00:12:16,540 --> 00:12:18,230
thousands of times

235
00:12:18,410 --> 00:12:22,800
not to turn in your papers early.

236
00:12:23,290 --> 00:12:24,560
Well,

237
00:12:24,700 --> 00:12:26,170
don't get too complacent,

238
00:12:26,330 --> 00:12:28,140
or problems might arise.

239
00:12:29,130 --> 00:12:33,870
So why didn't Jiang Tian and Sheng Wang win any awards this time?

240
00:12:34,400 --> 00:12:35,190
Actually,

241
00:12:35,210 --> 00:12:38,070
they advanced to the next round of the competition.

242
00:12:40,250 --> 00:12:41,000
That's right.

243
00:12:41,000 --> 00:12:41,970
They made it

244
00:12:42,080 --> 00:12:44,780
into the last 20 spots for the training camp.

245
00:12:44,960 --> 00:12:46,100
After the training,

246
00:12:46,120 --> 00:12:47,540
they will participate in the finals.

247
00:12:47,540 --> 00:12:49,640
If they place in the finals,

248
00:12:49,920 --> 00:12:50,690
they will receive awards

249
00:12:50,690 --> 00:12:52,350
for the entire Taiwan region.

250
00:12:52,370 --> 00:12:53,770
Even if they don't place,

251
00:12:53,910 --> 00:12:56,040
they will still receive an Excellence Award.

252
00:12:56,040 --> 00:12:58,020
Jiang Tian ranked 11th

253
00:12:58,190 --> 00:13:00,150
and Sheng Wang ranked 5th.

254
00:13:00,750 --> 00:13:02,180
They were only

255
00:13:02,440 --> 00:13:03,870
2 points apart.

256
00:13:03,920 --> 00:13:05,810
The students who placed between them

257
00:13:05,810 --> 00:13:07,460
were from the First School.

258
00:13:07,910 --> 00:13:09,190
But it's okay.

259
00:13:09,350 --> 00:13:11,240
Each of them

260
00:13:11,270 --> 00:13:12,170
has already

261
00:13:12,250 --> 00:13:13,100
secured a spot

262
00:13:13,200 --> 00:13:15,200
for early admission to university.

263
00:13:18,660 --> 00:13:19,920
Fifth place in Taiwan.

264
00:13:20,000 --> 00:13:20,800
No.5!

265
00:13:20,840 --> 00:13:22,670
Five, eleven. Eleven and five.

266
00:13:25,670 --> 00:13:26,520
Hey, Jing.

267
00:13:28,270 --> 00:13:31,200
Didn't you say you would come after Jiang Tian and me?

268
00:13:32,580 --> 00:13:33,600
Come after?

269
00:13:33,710 --> 00:13:35,840
You can't have your cake and eat it too.

270
00:13:37,060 --> 00:13:38,330
Sheng, you're so amazing.

271
00:13:38,330 --> 00:13:39,770
What gods do you worship? Tell me.

272
00:13:39,770 --> 00:13:41,160
And tell me what you like to eat.

273
00:13:41,160 --> 00:13:42,220
I want to try it too.

274
00:14:03,330 --> 00:14:04,460
Okay, everyone,

275
00:14:04,570 --> 00:14:06,500
you can start your self-study now.

276
00:14:09,160 --> 00:14:10,320
Everyone!

277
00:14:10,460 --> 00:14:11,950
One, two, three.

278
00:14:21,460 --> 00:14:24,880
Sheng. Tian.

279
00:14:24,910 --> 00:14:28,140
Five, eleven.

280
00:14:30,380 --> 00:14:31,280
Awesome!

281
00:14:33,630 --> 00:14:36,300
[Class A Grade 2]

