283
00:14:54,920 --> 00:14:57,250
Students on duty, please help me put away the rackets.

284
00:14:57,250 --> 00:14:59,160
Class is over!

285
00:15:08,410 --> 00:15:11,140
Hurry up and get changed. We're going to head out.

286
00:15:11,330 --> 00:15:12,280
What's wrong?

287
00:15:13,380 --> 00:15:14,460
Oh, nothing.

288
00:15:24,000 --> 00:15:24,870
What are you doing?

289
00:15:24,870 --> 00:15:25,540
Let's go.

290
00:15:25,900 --> 00:15:26,620
Get changed.

291
00:15:26,620 --> 00:15:27,220
Okay.

292
00:15:40,400 --> 00:15:41,230
Hey.

293
00:15:41,410 --> 00:15:42,360
Do you remember?

294
00:15:42,630 --> 00:15:45,360
We did this at the start of the school year as well.

295
00:15:45,420 --> 00:15:47,080
We were also going to the cafe.

296
00:15:47,080 --> 00:15:48,380
But how do you pronounce the name of that place?

297
00:15:48,380 --> 00:15:49,370
I still don't know.

298
00:15:49,370 --> 00:15:50,390
Alors.

299
00:15:50,420 --> 00:15:51,190
It's French.

300
00:15:51,370 --> 00:15:52,160
French?

301
00:15:52,250 --> 00:15:53,680
It means "so."

302
00:15:53,920 --> 00:15:55,540
I think what they are trying to express

303
00:15:55,540 --> 00:15:57,000
is to cherish the present.

304
00:15:57,290 --> 00:15:58,490
Cherish the present.

305
00:15:58,500 --> 00:15:59,130
And then,

306
00:15:59,200 --> 00:16:00,400
you mentioned living at school.

307
00:16:00,400 --> 00:16:01,950
And you actually moved into the school.

308
00:16:01,950 --> 00:16:02,850
So did you.

309
00:16:03,670 --> 00:16:04,800
Where is Jiang Tian?

310
00:16:04,830 --> 00:16:05,470
Tian!

311
00:16:06,470 --> 00:16:07,970
He disappeared just now.

312
00:16:08,420 --> 00:16:09,620
I didn't see him after we left school.

313
00:16:09,620 --> 00:16:10,950
I didn't see him either.

314
00:16:11,250 --> 00:16:12,760
It's okay. He's not a kid.

315
00:16:12,790 --> 00:16:14,200
And he's familiar with Xi and Lin.

316
00:16:14,200 --> 00:16:15,490
He'll find his way there on his own.

317
00:16:15,490 --> 00:16:16,240
Let's go.

318
00:16:16,770 --> 00:16:18,300
I need to go to the bathroom.

319
00:16:18,420 --> 00:16:19,190
Sheng,

320
00:16:19,240 --> 00:16:21,790
you're not trying to escape because you're supposed to treat us, are you?

321
00:16:21,790 --> 00:16:22,580
What are you talking about?

322
00:16:22,580 --> 00:16:24,840
Do you think Sheng is that kind of person?

323
00:16:25,090 --> 00:16:25,740
Sheng!

324
00:16:28,040 --> 00:16:28,700
Where is he?

325
00:16:31,820 --> 00:16:32,540
How is that possible?

326
00:16:32,540 --> 00:16:33,920
Sheng, stop hiding. Come out.

327
00:16:33,920 --> 00:16:34,960
How is that possible?

328
00:16:34,960 --> 00:16:35,920
It's okay, just come out.

329
00:16:35,920 --> 00:16:36,500
Just come out.

330
00:16:36,500 --> 00:16:38,360
How about you go down and find him?

331
00:16:38,790 --> 00:16:39,770
You go.

332
00:16:39,790 --> 00:16:40,420
What if I can't get back up later?

333
00:16:40,420 --> 00:16:42,170
The view here is really nice, though.

334
00:16:42,170 --> 00:16:42,570
Right.

335
00:16:42,570 --> 00:16:44,070
Did you bring your camera?

336
00:16:45,920 --> 00:16:46,850
Wait a minute.

337
00:16:46,950 --> 00:16:50,280
Come on, let's take a photo secretly while Sheng is not here.

338
00:16:50,910 --> 00:16:53,090
It's just like last time.

339
00:16:53,210 --> 00:16:54,820
Okay. One, two, three.

340
00:16:56,450 --> 00:16:57,200
Excuse me.

341
00:17:02,850 --> 00:17:04,849
Excuse me, have you seen Jiang Tian?

342
00:17:05,200 --> 00:17:06,180
Oh, thank you.

343
00:17:13,280 --> 00:17:14,790
Hey, have you seen Jiang Tian?

344
00:17:14,790 --> 00:17:15,390
No.

345
00:17:15,420 --> 00:17:16,310
Oh, thank you.

346
00:17:20,250 --> 00:17:21,780
Hey, have you seen Jiang Tian?

347
00:17:21,780 --> 00:17:22,930
I just saw him

348
00:17:22,950 --> 00:17:24,270
in the gym, I think.

349
00:17:24,490 --> 00:17:25,210
Gym?

350
00:17:25,230 --> 00:17:25,910
Yes.

351
00:17:26,329 --> 00:17:26,990
Oh, thank you.

352
00:17:26,990 --> 00:17:27,920
You're welcome.

353
00:17:49,620 --> 00:17:50,410
Jiang Tian.

354
00:17:52,250 --> 00:17:53,650
What are you looking for?

355
00:17:54,560 --> 00:17:55,460
Something.

356
00:17:57,280 --> 00:17:59,570
Don't forget we're having dinner with Xi.

357
00:17:59,570 --> 00:18:00,500
What are you looking for? Let me help you.

358
00:18:00,500 --> 00:18:01,700
Why should I tell you?

359
00:18:07,610 --> 00:18:08,400
I...

360
00:18:08,950 --> 00:18:10,710
I thought we were friends.

361
00:18:13,920 --> 00:18:14,580
No need.

362
00:18:16,710 --> 00:18:17,470
It's dirty.

363
00:18:26,040 --> 00:18:27,440
What are you looking for?

364
00:18:29,330 --> 00:18:30,190
No need.

365
00:18:30,960 --> 00:18:32,000
Just tell me what you're looking for.

366
00:18:32,000 --> 00:18:33,010
I can help you.

367
00:18:33,120 --> 00:18:34,070
It's okay.

368
00:18:37,650 --> 00:18:38,520
Ticket wallet.

369
00:18:39,580 --> 00:18:40,410
You're amazing.

370
00:18:40,410 --> 00:18:41,720
What gods do you worship? Tell me.

371
00:18:41,720 --> 00:18:43,250
And tell me what you like to eat.

372
00:18:43,250 --> 00:18:44,310
I want to try it too.

373
00:18:59,500 --> 00:19:00,650
Class is over!

374
00:19:01,200 --> 00:19:02,790
Students on duty, please help me put away the rackets.

375
00:19:02,790 --> 00:19:03,650
What's wrong?

376
00:19:05,210 --> 00:19:06,140
Nothing.

377
00:19:08,580 --> 00:19:09,440
So,

378
00:19:09,920 --> 00:19:11,410
you're doing it for me.

379
00:19:15,570 --> 00:19:16,360
Why?

380
00:19:23,160 --> 00:19:25,960
I think there must be something important inside.

381
00:19:29,560 --> 00:19:31,220
I guess it's an amulet, right?

382
00:19:32,410 --> 00:19:33,870
But I find it ridiculous

383
00:19:34,080 --> 00:19:34,790
to put your hopes in something

384
00:19:34,790 --> 00:19:36,550
you don't even know what it is.

385
00:19:40,050 --> 00:19:41,320
But then I thought,

386
00:19:41,610 --> 00:19:43,050
without it,

387
00:19:44,330 --> 00:19:46,260
what if you fall outside the top 30?

388
00:19:47,520 --> 00:19:48,680
Actually,

389
00:19:49,250 --> 00:19:50,720
it's not an amulet.

390
00:19:52,910 --> 00:19:53,690
Found it!

391
00:19:54,520 --> 00:19:55,360
Is this it?

392
00:20:01,100 --> 00:20:02,560
Check if it's still there.

393
00:20:12,340 --> 00:20:13,160
I forgot.

394
00:20:13,760 --> 00:20:15,290
You are picky and high-maintenance.

395
00:20:15,290 --> 00:20:16,950
You probably wouldn't want it

396
00:20:17,250 --> 00:20:18,980
since it was found here, right?

397
00:20:22,040 --> 00:20:22,770
Give it to me.

398
00:20:24,230 --> 00:20:25,130
It's dirty.

399
00:20:35,120 --> 00:20:36,120
It's still there.

400
00:20:38,500 --> 00:20:39,210
Thank you.

401
00:20:48,830 --> 00:20:50,760
Hey, there are people inside here!

402
00:20:56,380 --> 00:20:59,070
The security staff must not have noticed that there were people inside,

403
00:20:59,070 --> 00:21:00,010
so they locked it.

404
00:21:00,010 --> 00:21:01,210
What should we do now?

405
00:21:03,910 --> 00:21:06,240
Let me see if there are any tools to open it.

406
00:21:09,840 --> 00:21:11,300
Why not just call someone?

407
00:21:14,200 --> 00:21:15,260
There's no signal.

408
00:21:15,710 --> 00:21:18,440
No wonder you didn't reply to my message earlier.

409
00:21:19,700 --> 00:21:21,450
Didn't Sheng just go to the bathroom?

410
00:21:21,450 --> 00:21:22,120
It's taking way too long.

411
00:21:22,120 --> 00:21:23,170
Yes.

412
00:21:23,290 --> 00:21:25,120
He didn't really run away, did he?

413
00:21:25,120 --> 00:21:25,840
Hey.

414
00:21:26,480 --> 00:21:28,000
I'm just kidding. Why are you angry?

415
00:21:28,000 --> 00:21:29,410
You just said he wouldn't do that.

416
00:21:29,410 --> 00:21:30,470
What are you doing?

417
00:21:30,750 --> 00:21:32,150
We're waiting for Sheng.

418
00:21:32,420 --> 00:21:33,990
Sheng Wang won't come.

419
00:21:34,170 --> 00:21:35,100
How did you know?

420
00:21:35,170 --> 00:21:37,950
Because I just saw him heading towards the classroom,

421
00:21:37,950 --> 00:21:40,400
He must be going to get ready for evening study.

422
00:21:40,400 --> 00:21:41,280
I'm leaving now.

423
00:21:41,280 --> 00:21:41,890
Bye.

424
00:21:44,640 --> 00:21:45,750
-How is that possible?
-Evening study?

425
00:21:45,750 --> 00:21:48,380
Right. Didn't we agree to go to the cafe?

426
00:21:49,340 --> 00:21:50,190
Come on.

427
00:21:50,330 --> 00:21:52,310
The thing is, Sheng is missing now,

428
00:21:52,330 --> 00:21:53,960
and we don't know if Tian will be there.

429
00:21:53,960 --> 00:21:55,290
Should we keep waiting?

430
00:21:55,910 --> 00:21:57,510
Or should I call Sheng first?

431
00:21:57,520 --> 00:21:58,560
Okay.

432
00:22:07,210 --> 00:22:08,610
It went to the voicemail.

433
00:22:09,750 --> 00:22:11,430
Why don't you call Xi first and let him know?

434
00:22:11,430 --> 00:22:12,250
Okay.

435
00:22:18,370 --> 00:22:19,910
Isn't Jenny coming today?

436
00:22:20,700 --> 00:22:23,860
She said that if she comes, the students won't dare to have fun.

437
00:22:23,860 --> 00:22:25,860
Students have always been like that

438
00:22:26,000 --> 00:22:28,930
when they see their teachers—like mice seeing a cat.

439
00:22:29,080 --> 00:22:30,400
So, why are we here?

440
00:22:31,290 --> 00:22:33,220
Do you think we look like teachers?

441
00:22:34,080 --> 00:22:35,470
You don't.

442
00:22:36,430 --> 00:22:37,510
I'm glad I don't.

443
00:22:37,540 --> 00:22:38,890
It'd be worse if I did.

444
00:22:39,420 --> 00:22:40,680
Like Big Mouth Xu?

445
00:22:40,870 --> 00:22:42,070
No thanks.

446
00:22:50,120 --> 00:22:50,870
Hello?

447
00:22:52,710 --> 00:22:53,500
What?

448
00:22:55,180 --> 00:22:56,380
They're not here yet.

449
00:22:58,490 --> 00:22:59,360
Okay, I got it.

450
00:23:00,120 --> 00:23:02,380
I'll let you know as soon as I get any news.

451
00:23:03,170 --> 00:23:03,970
What's wrong?

452
00:23:04,310 --> 00:23:05,480
Jiang Tian and Sheng Wang are missing.

453
00:23:05,480 --> 00:23:07,140
The students can't find them.

454
00:23:07,530 --> 00:23:08,990
I'll go and help find them.

455
00:23:12,040 --> 00:23:12,970
I'll go with you.

456
00:23:18,580 --> 00:23:19,710
What should we do?

457
00:23:21,670 --> 00:23:23,040
Where is there a signal?

458
00:23:26,320 --> 00:23:27,390
It's gone again.

459
00:23:35,350 --> 00:23:36,030
Don't move.

460
00:23:38,350 --> 00:23:39,150
What's wrong?

461
00:23:47,240 --> 00:23:48,440
Jiang... Jiang Tian,

462
00:23:48,690 --> 00:23:49,750
what are you doing?

463
00:23:50,390 --> 00:23:52,050
A big cockroach is behind you.

464
00:23:52,670 --> 00:23:54,000
I've got it pinned down.

465
00:23:54,880 --> 00:23:56,370
Slowly come this way.

466
00:24:00,600 --> 00:24:01,220
Sheng...

467
00:24:06,670 --> 00:24:09,200
Did you catch it?

468
00:24:09,290 --> 00:24:09,960
Yes.

469
00:24:10,420 --> 00:24:12,550
Sheng Wang. Jiang Tian.

470
00:24:23,430 --> 00:24:24,290
What happened?

471
00:24:25,040 --> 00:24:26,170
We lost something.

472
00:24:26,670 --> 00:24:28,670
When we were looking for it just now,

473
00:24:29,040 --> 00:24:32,300
it seems the security staff accidentally locked the door.

474
00:24:33,210 --> 00:24:34,630
Luckily, your classmates were proactive enough

475
00:24:34,630 --> 00:24:35,400
to find you.

476
00:24:35,990 --> 00:24:37,230
Otherwise, you two

477
00:24:37,580 --> 00:24:39,710
would have had to spend the night here.

478
00:24:40,670 --> 00:24:41,870
I'm glad you're fine.

479
00:24:42,330 --> 00:24:42,890
Hey, Lin.

480
00:24:42,920 --> 00:24:43,360
Yes?

481
00:24:43,660 --> 00:24:46,190
Send a text to let everyone know we found them.

482
00:24:46,780 --> 00:24:48,580
I bet everyone must be starving.

483
00:24:49,820 --> 00:24:50,620
I'm starving.

484
00:24:50,780 --> 00:24:51,700
Let's go and eat first.

485
00:24:51,700 --> 00:24:52,320
Let's go.

486
00:24:52,650 --> 00:24:54,580
Hey, did you guys order in advance?

487
00:24:54,960 --> 00:24:55,930
It's all ready.

488
00:24:56,520 --> 00:24:57,980
We're waiting for you two.

489
00:24:59,790 --> 00:25:00,850
It was all my fault.

490
00:25:00,880 --> 00:25:01,590
Let's go.

491
00:25:06,830 --> 00:25:08,990
Come on, let's drink tea instead of wine

492
00:25:08,990 --> 00:25:12,410
to celebrate Sheng Wang and Jiang Tian making it to the finals of the English competition.

493
00:25:12,410 --> 00:25:13,080
Cheers!

494
00:25:13,210 --> 00:25:15,760
Cheers!

495
00:25:18,790 --> 00:25:20,500
Next time, if anyone gets a good ranking,

496
00:25:20,500 --> 00:25:21,460
the treat will be on me.

497
00:25:21,460 --> 00:25:22,390
Okay!

498
00:25:22,850 --> 00:25:25,810
Sheng, go! Tian, go!

499
00:25:26,020 --> 00:25:27,970
Here! Go, go, go!

500
00:25:28,240 --> 00:25:30,190
Go! Go! Go!

501
00:25:30,620 --> 00:25:31,370
Finish it.

502
00:25:34,040 --> 00:25:35,630
-What?
-Cheers.

503
00:25:41,750 --> 00:25:43,150
Wow, it looks delicious.

504
00:25:49,530 --> 00:25:51,160
Drink up. Cheers.

505
00:25:51,180 --> 00:25:52,640
I'll go get some more food.

506
00:25:58,280 --> 00:25:59,520
Where is Lin going?

507
00:26:00,840 --> 00:26:02,330
He's afraid there won't be enough food,

508
00:26:02,330 --> 00:26:03,730
so he's going to get more.

509
00:26:04,040 --> 00:26:05,540
Seriously?

510
00:26:05,710 --> 00:26:06,860
We're not gluttons.

511
00:26:06,920 --> 00:26:08,320
And there are girls here.

512
00:26:08,380 --> 00:26:10,710
They're always talking about dieting.

513
00:26:10,910 --> 00:26:12,510
One minute they're fasting,

514
00:26:12,750 --> 00:26:14,730
the next they're on some extreme diet.

515
00:26:14,730 --> 00:26:16,040
They won't eat too much.

516
00:26:16,040 --> 00:26:17,960
Who are you talking about?

517
00:26:18,070 --> 00:26:19,060
You hit too hard.

518
00:26:19,080 --> 00:26:19,860
So what?

519
00:26:22,910 --> 00:26:23,560
What?

520
00:26:23,630 --> 00:26:24,550
Were you just trying to hit a girl?

521
00:26:24,550 --> 00:26:25,660
Were you just trying to hit the class monitor?

522
00:26:25,660 --> 00:26:26,610
Yes.

523
00:26:26,710 --> 00:26:28,660
You don't need to fast or go on some extreme diet.

524
00:26:28,660 --> 00:26:30,860
You eat more than all the boys, alright?

525
00:26:31,490 --> 00:26:33,080
Big eater!

526
00:26:34,030 --> 00:26:34,600
Stupid.

527
00:26:34,630 --> 00:26:35,640
He wants to die.

528
00:26:37,080 --> 00:26:38,090
Quite popular.

529
00:26:40,290 --> 00:26:41,070
Me?

530
00:26:41,900 --> 00:26:42,830
What do you mean?

531
00:26:43,420 --> 00:26:45,690
A girl chasing someone all around

532
00:26:46,100 --> 00:26:49,520
just because he said she eats more than the boys in front of you.

533
00:26:49,520 --> 00:26:50,850
Why do you think that is?

534
00:26:56,950 --> 00:26:58,100
Troublemaker.

535
00:27:00,510 --> 00:27:02,310
What does that have to do with me?

536
00:27:06,870 --> 00:27:07,770
Gosh!

537
00:27:07,820 --> 00:27:09,100
Let's call a truce.

538
00:27:09,290 --> 00:27:09,830
I'm starving.

539
00:27:09,830 --> 00:27:10,350
Shall we eat something first?

540
00:27:10,350 --> 00:27:11,740
Watch your mouth.

541
00:27:12,250 --> 00:27:14,410
If you're hungry, just eat and drink as much as you can.

542
00:27:14,410 --> 00:27:16,000
Today, Sheng Wang is treating.

543
00:27:16,000 --> 00:27:17,930
Right, I'm treating. Enjoy.

544
00:27:17,950 --> 00:27:19,110
Thank you, Sheng.

545
00:27:21,470 --> 00:27:22,120
Gao,

546
00:27:22,310 --> 00:27:25,340
being chased by Pepper is better than being chased by Big Mouth Xu, right?

547
00:27:25,340 --> 00:27:25,970
Exactly.

548
00:27:26,000 --> 00:27:26,820
I guess so.

549
00:27:29,170 --> 00:27:29,970
Sorry, Little Mouth,

550
00:27:29,970 --> 00:27:30,750
for insulting your dad.

551
00:27:30,750 --> 00:27:31,840
Haha.

552
00:27:32,750 --> 00:27:33,840
It's okay.

553
00:27:33,960 --> 00:27:35,250
Anyway, when I'm out here playing,

554
00:27:35,250 --> 00:27:37,380
I always cut off ties with my dad first.

555
00:27:38,570 --> 00:27:40,640
Plus, I heard last time

556
00:27:40,870 --> 00:27:42,580
he caught a guy who went online secretly

557
00:27:42,580 --> 00:27:43,790
When they took him to the Student Affairs,

558
00:27:43,790 --> 00:27:45,170
he was wearing a black plastic bag on his head.

559
00:27:45,170 --> 00:27:46,280
That's not the scariest part.

560
00:27:46,280 --> 00:27:48,500
Last time, when I went to the office to help a teacher grade exam papers,

561
00:27:48,500 --> 00:27:51,000
I heard that someone next door got caught dating.

562
00:27:51,000 --> 00:27:54,130
Then his dad called both families to arrange a marriage.

563
00:27:54,270 --> 00:27:56,410
They were so scared they broke up on the spot.

564
00:27:56,410 --> 00:27:57,310
A marriage?

565
00:27:57,330 --> 00:27:58,120
Yes.

566
00:27:58,200 --> 00:27:59,100
That's crazy.

567
00:27:59,200 --> 00:27:59,950
Yes.

568
00:28:00,370 --> 00:28:01,900
From now on, he is not my dad.

569
00:28:02,090 --> 00:28:03,370
